        </div>
        <div>
            <h2 class="font-robot text-3xl font-black mb-8 uppercase tracking-tighter">Hogyan működik a technológia?</h2>
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="flex gap-6">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-purple-500/20 text-purple-500"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
                    <div><h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Adatbányászat</h4><p class="text-sm text-gray-500">0-24 órás globális piacfigyelés és statisztikai elemzés.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-6">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-purple-500/20 text-purple-500"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
