                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-6">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-purple-500/20 text-purple-500"><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i></div>
                    <div><h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Személyre szabott matek</h4><p class="text-sm text-gray-500">A robot kiszámolja a tétet a tőkéd alapján (Drawdown protection).</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="matek" class="py-20 bg-zinc-900/30 border-y border-white/5">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <h2 class="font-robot text-3xl font-black mb-12 uppercase tracking-tighter">A matek, ami helyetted dolgozik</h2>
            <div class="bg-black/50 p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-purple-500/20 purple-glow">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold mb-2 tracking-widest">Példa induló tőke</p>
                        <div class="text-5xl font-black text-white">100.000 Ft</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                        <div class="text-purple-500 font-bold mb-1">12 hónapos iránycél:</div>
                        <div class="text-5xl font-black gradient-text">1.400.000 Ft+</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-8 text-xs text-gray-600 italic">"A titok a dinamikus kamatos kamat. Az AI nem összegekkel, hanem százalékkal dolgozik."</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="arak" class="py-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="font-robot text-4xl font-black mb-4 uppercase">Válassz okosan</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500">Ez nem tagsági díj, hanem befektetés a technológiába.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-purple-600 p-1 rounded-[3rem] shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(168,85,247,0.3)]">
            <div class="bg-black rounded-[2.9rem] p-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-10">
                <div class="text-left">
                    <h3 class="font-robot text-3xl font-black mb-2 uppercase">Havi Licenc</h3>
                    <p class="text-purple-400 font-bold mb-6">Minden funkció elérhető</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check text-purple-500 mr-2"></i> Skyhigh.Ai Dashboard</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check text-purple-500 mr-2"></i> Napi 1 Master Tipp</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check text-purple-500 mr-2"></i> MLM Jutalék rendszer (2%)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="text-5xl font-black mb-4">20.000 Ft<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">/hó</span></div>
                    <button class="w-full bg-purple-600 px-10 py-4 rounded-2xl font-black hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition uppercase tracking-widest">Kérem a hozzáférést</button>
